Return a compact table (max 20 rows) of these per-(cmdb_id,kpi_name) records sorted by num_points_exceeding_threshold desc, then anomaly_ratio desc. Also include counts of how many (cmdb_id,kpi_name) pairs have num_points_exceeding_threshold > 0. Return results as JSON-serializable dict.
